Abia State Governor Okezie Ikpeazu has signed into law the 2022 Appropriation Bill of N147, 282, 196, 200. The budget has a Capital Expenditure Profile of N79, 779, 887, 500. The Recurrent Expenditure has an outlay of N67, 502, 318, 700.   ‘Agric ministry spent N3.8b on Ruga scheme without…     Gbajabiamila welcomes first babies of year     Nigerians have suffered enough, NLC tells Fed Govt   Ikpeazu on December 14 presented the Appropriation Bill to the House of Assembly. - Advertisement - He expressed gratitude to the Speaker and members for the expeditious review and passage of the Bill.